{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the one, that's my aunt that waited for me when I came back from the summer camp, [NON-ENGLISH] Topcha.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we never saw her again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was left with my mother alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother worked in a factory being a seamstress, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She knew, she knew how to use a machine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So through some friends, she got that job in the factory also as a, working as a machinist.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Everybody had to work, no matter how old you were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I managed to get into a factory, to a fur factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of my father's uncles was a-- two brothers, they were fur merchants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], very rich people before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His brother-- he had another brother that left for Palestine at that time, before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember the story they were telling about [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Her name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She drove him crazy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She wanted to go to-- she said, I don't-- this was a constant saying in the family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I kept repeating what she said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't want my body to wander after I'm dead to Mother Rachel's tomb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want to be buried there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So since he was a rich man, he could afford it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They went to Palestine before the war, I think in 1936.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember I used to be scared of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was a tall man with a long, brown beard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And sure enough, six months after they arrived, she died, and she's buried near Mother Rachel's tomb.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this other brother, [NON-ENGLISH], he worked at that factory as a-- he was, they were dyeing furs there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, everything, all the furs were done for the army, for the German army.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
